Abstract = {Using SIPRI data on all international transfers of major conventional
   weapons 1950-2007, we study the relationship between differences in
   polity and arms trade. To study whether states tend to trade arms within
   their political vicinity we estimate gravity models of the likelihood of
   trade at the bilateral level and study the evolution of the global
